#: 0c26108bdb5e4a9893f7f3d32cd1604e
msgid ""
"This is a brief introduction to using Qubes Builder v2 to work with Qubes OS"
" sources. It will walk you through installing and configuring Builder v2, "
"and using it to fetch and build Qubes OS packages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/building/qubes-builder-v2.rst:7
#: e2e98fda8ddf4c3baff1df7323fc8eab
msgid ""
